{
  "stem": "1354.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but my brother-in-law, they choosed him too-- because she was married-- they choosed him to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lived through the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because after the war, I never saw him, but when we came, after the war, to Krakow, we went to the house, and there was a janitor.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She told us that he came back, and he asked or anybody is alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time I-- that was ghetto B where we lived, so my brother found a place for us in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was still-- then Schindler decided when they start liquidating ghetto, Schindler decided to build the living quarters, the barracks, in the back of the factory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went just for a short time to-- to Plaszow until they built-- until they built the living quarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was that like?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was-- it was barracks just like in Plaszow, or-- but we were going-- we had a little bit better food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not afraid like in Plaszow that you never-- that death will come on the balcony and-- and shoot you while you working.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we just worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I worked hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were making pots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was one place what they were making them from scratch, and then I was where they were painting them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were booths with-- with paint inside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Polish people were coming there too, to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a guy was standing and-- and painting those big, sometimes big pots, sometimes little ones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my job was to bring big boards with nails on them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
